[Name] KDF
[Summary] Displays the available file devices and their capacity.
[Description] KDiskFree displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, floppy and CD/DVD drives, etc.) along with information on their capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and unmount drives and view them in a file manager.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL), Version 2.
[Homepage] http://utils.kde.org/projects/kdf/
